                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Quasi-monochromatic linearly polarized gamma-ray",
                "beams were produced from laser Compton backscattering",
                "of free-electron laser photons off relativistic",
                "electrons. The resulting gamma-ray beam is nearly",
                "mono-energetic and almost 100% circularly polarized.",
                "The beam intensity on the target was up to 3E+7 phot/s"
